    - target: {fileID: 5420115657269891386, guid: 5ddd7e9d3f12a9a439a2e2c43e7cb1ab, type: 3}
      propertyPath: m_text
      value: "The game is played exclusively virtually due to the distances between
        the various planets through other planet\u2019s equivalents of VR headsets.
        The most prestigious competition is known as the Integalactic Championship.
        This is the first time Earth participates in this tournament. The game is
        played through avatars called Konchi. The appearance of each Konchi is incredibly
        important as it has a lot of cultural significance."
      objectReference: {fileID: 0}
